            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lamb keema pav</strong> between the<strong> buttered brioche halves </strong>with the <strong>turmeric roast potatoes</strong> and <strong>tomato & red onion salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish the lamb keema pav with the <strong>remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
